### Usage 

Install all needed files with 

```python

pip3 install -r requirements.txt

```

later run python3 send_mail.py --config 

Here you are going to configure the SMTP, host(mail), password, and port you are going to send the email via cli. 

On gmail just use a app password it will work fine

to run just use python3 send_mail.py -m "Hello"

you can send attachments, change subject etc on the options. 